{"word":"προσεύχομαι","slug":"προσεύχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσεύχομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to offer prayers</i> or <i>vows</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <el>πρ. τὸν θεόν</el> <i>to address</i> him <i>in prayer</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to offer prayers, to worship</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>πρ. τι</el> <i>to pray for</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}